OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHundreds of NHS buildings  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcontain asbestos, says TUC 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of NHS buildings across London
OL,6, and Scotland still contain asbestos,   
OL,7, the Trades Union Congress has warned.  
OL,9,FThe substance, which can cause cancer, 
OL,10,Fwas present in at least 451 NHS        
OL,11,Fpremises in London and 695 in Scotland,
OL,12,Fresearch for the TUC found.            
OL,14,FTwo-thirds of these buildings, which   
OL,15,Fincluded hospitals, health centres, GP 
OL,16,Fsurgeries and blood donor clinics, were
OL,17,Fopen to the public, it added.          
OL,19,FThe TUC wants all asbestos to be       
OL,20,Fremoved from public buildings by law.  
